These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, entrepreneur, mechanic, paramedic, photographer, social-worker, videographer
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, montecristo, game, ritmeester, aristoff, cain, siglo
 1. the paramedic is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is the paramedic##1
 3. the videographer is on the right of the social-worker##1
 4. the game-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 5. the mechanic is in the middle##1
 6. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the photographer is the old-henry-smoker##1
 8. the electrician is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 9. the game-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
10. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the mechanic##1
11. the videographer is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | photographer | paramedic | entrepreneur | mechanic | electrician | social-worker | videographer |
| Cigar   | old-henry    | aristoff   | ritmeester      | cain | game    | montecristo    | siglo         |

