.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, eggplant, nectarine, peach, raspberry, watermelon
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, malaysian, russian, polish, australian, turkish, colombian
 1. the australian is the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the colombian##1
 3. the turkish is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the malaysian##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the australian is in the middle##1
 8. the australian is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the colombian is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | cranberry | cucumber | peach | nectarine | raspberry | watermelon | eggplant |
| Nationality   | malaysian      | russian   | polish   | australian      | brazilian       | colombian       | turkish     |

