.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, sunflower, dahlia, daffodil, lily, poppy, orchid
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, freelancer, mechanic, photographer, scientist, teacher, writer
 1. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 2. the person who growslily is on the left of the writer##1
 3. the freelancer is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the bartender is the person who growslily##1
 6. the mechanic is on the right of the freelancer##1
 7. the freelancer is on the left of the mechanic##1
 8. the freelancer is on the right of the photographer##1
 9. the person who growspoppy is the photographer##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the photographer is in the middle##1
12. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Flower   | sunflower | lily     | dahlia  | poppy       | balloon-flower       | orchid  | daffodil   |
| Job    | teacher  | bartender | writer | photographer | freelancer | mechanic | scientist |

