.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: disco, folk, indie, jazz, metal, r&b, rock
City: edinburgh, nizza, new-york, marseilles, liverpool, colone, boston
 1. the fan of metal is the person traveling to nizza##1
 2. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 3. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 5. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 6. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 8. the fan of indie is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 9. the fan of indie is the person traveling to liverpool##1
10. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the fan of folk##1
11. the person traveling to boston is the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | rock     | jazz     | indie      | folk | metal      | disco     |
| City   | marseilles | new-york | colone | liverpool | boston | nizza | edinburgh |

