.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, drawing, gardening, magic-tricks, sudoku, video-games
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, egyptian, nigerian, argentine, japanese, australian, russian
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is the russian##1
 2. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the australian is in the middle##1
 4. the japanese is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the japanese is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the canadian##1
 7. the australian is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the japanese##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | cooking | drawing | sudoku     | gardening | video-games | magic-tricks | board-games |
| Nationality     | russian   | nigerian    | japanese | australian     | canadian         | argentine     | egyptian        |

