.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: r&b, blues, country, folk, hip-hop, disco, ambient
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, skateboard, tram, trike
 1. the fan of disco is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 2. the fan of r&b is the person driving the bus##1
 3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 5. the person driving the trike is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 6. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 7. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of country is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the fan of blues is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
10. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Music-Genre    | country | disco   | r&b | folk | ambient  | hip-hop | blues |
| Transport   | ship   | skateboard | bus | tram     | jet-ski | trike | quad-bike   |

