.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, drama, martial-arts, satire, time-travel
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, water, cola, 7up, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, sprite
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person drinking 7up##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | time-travel | drama | martial-arts | satire     | animation | crime |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate | 7up      | sprite | cola    | almond-milk | water   | coffee  |

