 4. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person watching horror movies##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
