.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-11::.
There 7 different types of food: lime, peas, pepper, potato, raspberry, spinach, tomato
7 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, mah-jongg, bridge, backgammon, poker, whist
 1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the far left##1
 3. the person eating potato is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 4. the person playing scrabble is the person eating pepper##1
 5. the person playing bridge is the person eating raspberry##1
 6. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 7. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 8. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1
10. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
11. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
12. the person playing whist is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |   4    |     5     |    6    |   7    |
| Food          | raspberry | lime     | spinach | pepper | peas      | tomato  | potato |
| Game   | bridge   | backgammon | mah-jongg  | scrabble | snooker | poker | whist   |

