4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the russian##1
5. the malaysian is on the right of the british##1
6. the thai is the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the pakistani is in the middle##1
8. the pakistani is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4     |    5    |     6     |      7      |
| Birthday      | march       | november    | july    | february       | august    | september   | january |
