.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-13::.
7 different pets are kept: fish, goldfish, hamster, turtle, chinchilla, goat, lizard
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, family, martial-arts, musical, romance, sports
 1. the person watching disaster movies is the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 4. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 5. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the person watching family movies is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the owner of the fish is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |    7     |
| Pet         | goat | goldfish   | lizard | fish | chinchilla | turtle | hamster  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts  | musical | sports  | family | romance | crime     | disaster |

