 7. the fan of country is the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the owner of the fish is on the left of the fan of country##1
 9. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
10. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of funk##1
11. the fan of punk is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |     4     |     5     |     6      |   7    |
| Music-Genre   | blues | funk | country  | pop | indie | punk | gospel |
| Pet           | lizard   | fish    | goldfish | goat      | frog      | chinchilla | pony   |

 